```plantuml
@startuml IBM_logdna-cos

participant "COS Bucket" as COS
participant "Serverless Function" as Function
participant "LogDNA API" as LogDNA
participant "Archive COS Bucket" as Archive

COS -> Function: Object Created Event
activate Function

Function -> COS: Download Log File
COS --> Function: Log File (Zipped)

Function -> Function: Unzip and Parse Logs
Function -> Function: Format Logs for LogDNA

loop For each batch (5000 logs)
    Function -> LogDNA: Send Logs (POST)
    alt Success
        LogDNA --> Function: 200 OK
    else Failure
        LogDNA --> Function: Error
        Function -> Function: Retry (3 attempts)
    end
end

Function -> Archive: Copy Processed File
Archive --> Function: Success
Function -> COS: Delete Original File
COS --> Function: Success

deactivate Function

@enduml
```